[Desktop Entry]
Version=1.0
Type=Application
Name=Wifite
Comment=WiFi auditor launcher — Full attacks + powerful offline "Crack Only" mode for previous handshakes (no monitor mode)
Icon=kali-wifite
Exec=/home/will/bin/wifite-launcher/launch.sh
Terminal=false
Categories=Network;Security;
Keywords=kali;wifi;wifite;handshake;pmkid;crack;aircrack;hashcat;pentest;wireless;
# Note: Internal WiFi (wlan0) is protected. Use external card (wlan1) for monitor mode attacks.
StartupNotify=true
X-GNOME-Autostart-enabled=false
NoDisplay=false

# Wifite Desktop Launcher
#
# Two powerful modes:
#
# 1. "Crack Handshakes Only (Offline)"  [the star feature]
#    - No monitor mode, no packet injection
#    - Scans any hs/ directory for .cap (4-way) and .22000 (PMKID) files
#    - Beautiful list with ESSID / BSSID / Type / Date
#    - Multi-select handshakes to crack
#    - Choose wordlist (auto-discovers rockyou, probable, fasttrack, wifite.txt etc.)
#    - One-click "Extract rockyou" helper for the gzipped version
#    - Choose tool: hashcat (recommended, handles PMKID + fast) or aircrack-ng
#    - Live output + progress while cracking
#    - Automatically saves successes to cracked.json (wifite format)
#
# 2. "Full Wifite Attack (Monitor Mode)"
#    - Configure common flags before launch (--kill, --random-mac, --pmkid, --wps-only, etc.)
#    - Pick wordlist + custom hs-dir
#    - Target filters (ESSID/BSSID/channel)
#    - "Pillage" (auto-attack after N seconds)
#    - Launches in a real terminal (best for interactive use)
#    - Command preview + "Copy command" button
#
# Also includes:
# - View previously cracked APs
# - Check any .cap file for handshakes (wifite --check)
# - Quick open hs/ folders
#
# For authorized testing only. Use responsibly.
